    "chemicalDescription": [
      "Methionyl sh-Oligopeptide-1 sr-Jellyfish Polypeptide-1 is a single chain recombinant fusion peptide, produced by fermentation in  E. coli.  The starting gene is synthesized by the fusion of the gene from sh-Oligopeptide-1 and sr-Jellyfish Polypeptide-1 with the initiation code for methionine. The fusion peptide contains 292 amino acids and consists of the proper sequence of the 20 standard amino acids"
